{"tid":404483,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有墨香愛好者","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T03:24:34.000Z","uid":78763,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf4b459958ae95831f9ed2324931e95a87f1f85","tid":404483,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"見近期冇乜私服好玩<br />\n諗住大家圍內開返隻圍圍喂 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*就算開放出去都會有圍內福利</span><br />\n唔收費 大家打裝或者定期搞活動派下箱<br />\n<br />\n暫定配置就 正服 既 10倍 屬於經典慢服 冇忍技 坦技<br />\n暫定計劃<br />\n-廢除自動打怪系統 ( 保留 自動回紅藍 )<br />\n-回復2008年墨香味道<br />\n<br />\n有興趣想一齊圍內玩既可以加入TG GROUP<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GXYcfkLSqNEzR26jjC7Q5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGXYcfkLSqNEzR26jjC7Q5w&d=dBg6tSW81F0Leg6ahdWzMZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=911b9e29\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GXYcfkLSqNEzR26jjC7Q5w</a><br />\n<br />\n有任何意見都可以係GROUP到提出<br />\n我會盡量去改<br />\n<br />\n最緊要大家玩得開心 <br />\n<br />\n致 墨香愛好者<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/o85904b1e1d297240a46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fo85904b1e1d297240a46.jpg&h=42ef24df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d1a01a4cfbb8de3c48bbd9ada209d7dc69bb4ec","tid":404483,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb61cdbe200f486c2886c6e81e3f9cca0cd9b426","tid":404483,"uid":11575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"有無咩特別裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6616dace8d98397e893cce3